I use SDL built from macports, with ocamlsdl built from godi (on my 13"
MacBook, which works quite well for me).  SDL isn't exactly a GUI toolkit
though, so you'd have to write your own widgets on top of it, or try to wrap
an existing set of sdl widgets written in C.

Ralph

